author: Danielle Wallace
title: Florida Easter cookout broken up by police amid coronavirus stay-at-home order
description: More than 100 people gathered outside an affordable housing complex in the Florida Panhandle for an Easter cookout Sunday, defying social distancing measures amid the coronavirus outbreak before police arrived to break up the scene.
